52.225-3, <I>Buy American Act-Construction Materials, </I>FAR 52.225-5.
<P><LI TYPE=A VALUE=7><B>(DEVIATION)</B><I> Certification and Disclosure
Regarding
Payments to Influence Certain Federal Transactions,</I> FAR 52.203-11, if the Prime Contract
contains the Clause entitled <I>Limitation on Payment to Influence Certain Federal
Transactions,</I> FAR
<P><LI TYPE=A VALUE=8><B>(DEVIATION) </B><I>Certification Regarding
