acceptance and
disposal of SNF.
<p>
<strong>[2]</strong> The Purchaser disposal contract is the legal agreement between the Federal Government and generators and
owners of spent nuclear fuel that prescribes the conditions and timing for pickup of spent nuclear fuel and its
transportation to a Federal facility. 
