<DOCNO>WT01-B16-66</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA027-000294-B016-52</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.uilondon.org:80/waste5.html 193.195.1.162 19970120074131 text/html 5610
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 1997 07:41:11 GMT
