<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT01-B16-72</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA027-000294-B016-162</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.uilondon.org:80/waste63.html 193.195.1.162 19970120074256 text/html 2445
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 1997 07:42:49 GMT
