<DOCHDR>
http://www.uilondon.org:80/uiabs95/akin.html 193.195.1.162 19970120074837 text/html 4867
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 1997 07:48:06 GMT
Server: Apache/0.8.14
