<DOCNO>WT01-B16-85</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA027-000294-B018-277</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.uilondon.org:80/uiabs95/glod.html 193.195.1.162 19970120075423 text/html 4712
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
