<IMG SRC="images/otorder.gif" ALT="How To Place An Order" WIDTH=355 HEIGHT=105><BR CLEAR=LEFT>
<TABLE BGCOLOR=CYAN WIDTH=100% BORDER=1 BORDERCOLOR=NAVY CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=3>
<TR><TH ALIGN=CENTER>
	<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE=2>
	<A HREF="#Online Forms">Ordering Online</A>  <A HREF="#Mail-In Forms">Ordering With A Mail-In Form</A>  <A HREF="#Payment Options">Payment Options</A><BR>
	<A HREF="#Tape Guarantee">Our Tape Guarantee</A>  <A HREF="#Shipping">Shipping Rates</A>  <A HREF="#Questions">Questions</A> 
</TH></TR>
</TABLE>
<BR>
<CENTER><TABLE WIDTH=100% BORDER=0 COLS=1>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE=2 COLOR=BLACK>Placing an order is easy!&nbsp&nbspYou may submit your order online, send it via U.S. Mail, <BR>or call our toll free phone number <B>(800-808-8173)</B>.<BR><BR><A HREF="#Online Forms">Order online</A> if you want to use your credit card to get your tapes <B><I>FAST!</I></B>&nbsp&nbspIf you would rather not submit your order online or would like to pay with a check, you may mail your order.&nbsp&nbspTo do this, you will need our <A HREF="mailin.htm">mail-in form</A>.&nbsp&nbspIf you would like a quote or have any questions, please feel free to call us (800-808-8173) and please mention OT Studios Online!<BR>&nbsp</TD></TR>
<TR><TH>
	<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE=4 COLOR=NAVY><A NAME="Online Forms"><IMG SRC="images/hr1.gif" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=26 ALT="-------------"><BR>
	<B> Ordering Online </B></A>
</TH></TR>
<TR><TD>
	<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE=2 COLOR=BLACK><BR>Ordering online is fast and <B><I>EASY!</I></B>&nbsp&nbspFirst, place a check mark next to the item(s) you wish to order:<BR><IMG SRC="images/select.gif" ALT="Selected Items - Example" WIDTH=568 HEIGHT=37 ALIGN=CENTER><BR CLEAR=LEFT><BR><IMG SRC="images/order.gif" ALT="Order Online Form - Example" WIDTH=463 HEIGHT=311 ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=5>Then, simply fill out the online order form which is located at the bottom of each page.<BR><BR>The fields denoted with an asterisk(*) are considered optional.  Both 'Phone' and 'Email' are optional, however we do ask that you provide us with at least one in case we need to contact you regarding your order.<BR><BR>Click the 'Submit Order' button to send your order to OT Studios. Your order will be quickly processed and shipped to you.<BR>&nbsp
</TD></TR>
<TR><TH>
	<FONT FACE="Arial, Helvetica" SIZE=4 COLOR=NAVY><A NAME="Mail-In Forms"><IMG SRC="images/hr1.gif" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=26 ALT="-------------"><BR>
