<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT01-B16-145</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA094-001008-B017-328</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://boca.sankyo.com:80/ccrs.htm 199.227.106.65 19970121154215 text/html 7173
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 15:43:36 GMT
Content-Type: text/html
