<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Chicken Pox</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY><P>After years of waiting, the chicken pox vaccine is here.
Children and adults no longer need to suffer with that itchy rash that can
scar for life. Children from twelve months to twelve years need only one
dose. If you are over twelve you will need a second dose.
<P>We also have all the usual vaccines available in our office including:
<UL><LI>Polio
