This form assumes that you are using a version 2.0 or later of 
NCSA Mosaic.  This form may not work with other browsers.
<p>

Messages can be posted one of two ways.
<OL>
<LI> Type text into the form below. The message will be retrieved using
the information in the recipient/subject field. 
<p>
<P>

<Form method=POST action="http://wwwrcamnl.wr.usgs.gov/cgi-bin/feedback-mail">

Please enter the subject:<BR>
<UL>
<inPUT NAME="username"><P>
</UL>

Please enter your email address:<BR>
<UL>
<inPUT NAME="realname"><P>
</OL>

<P>

Please enter your comments in the box below:<BR>
<TEXTAREA NAME="comments" ROWS=5 COLS=50></TEXTAREA><P>


<Input TYPE="submit" VALUE="Send this message">
<Input TYPE="reset" VALUE="Erase this message"><p>
<HR>
</Form>
<P>
<LI> All INTERNET mail sent to webmaster@mailrcamnl.wr.usgs.gov will be
delivered directly to the Webmaster.
</UL>

