<HR><!-- This file was created with the fm2html filter.The filter is copyright Norwegian Telecom Research and was programmed by Jon Stephenson von Tetzchner.  --><H1><A NAME="HDR0">OFFICE OF THE ASSISTANT CHIEF HYDROLOGIST FOR RESEARCH AND EXTERNAL COORDINATION <BR>
