<table width="90%" border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0">
 <tr>
  <td valign="top">
   <font face="arial" color="#ff0000" size="5"><strong>We digest it for you...</strong></font><br>
   <font size="3" face="arial"><img src="images/line.gif" width="30%" height="1">  
    <br>
    The <font color="#c80000">Digest</font> tracks the entire field--all the
    doctors' journals, research, conferences, and newsletters.  
    Then we summarize what is essential for you to know to get
    better and stay healthy.  We're your one-stop read for 
    what's new and effective in alternative medicine.
   </font>	
