    <font face="arial" size="2">
     <ul>
      <li><b><a href="i16-a42.shtml">High Blood PressureLower It Naturally</a></b> 
       <hr size="1" width="99%" color="#ff0000" align="left">
       Watch your high blood pressure drop to normal when you change your diet, take coenzyme Q10 and hawthorn, exercise, and release buried emotions, says cardiologist Stephen Sinatra, M.D.<br>
       <tt>By Richard Leviton</tt><p>

      <li><b><a href="i16-a48.shtml">Kelly LeBrock</a></b>
