       <tt>By Stephen E. Langer, M.D.</tt><p>

      <li><b><a href="i16-a58.shtml">Reversing Cancer Successfully</a></b>
       <hr size="1" width="99%" color="#ff0000" align="left">
       Physicians at American Metabolic Institute use up to 150 different nontoxic medications and therapies to teach the immune system to eliminate cancer.<br>

  <br><br>

